## üß™ Essential Equipment Matrix
A standardized laboratory powered by QTE Technologies integrates these core categories:

| Equipment Category | Key Components | Strategic Role |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Thermal Control** | Water Baths, Hot Plates | Precise sample incubation and heating. |
| **Cleaning & Prep** | Ultrasonic Cleaners | Micro-level contaminant removal. |
| **Sensing & IoT** | Smart Sensors (pH, Temp, Gas) | Real-time environmental monitoring. |
| **Mechanical Systems** | Precision Gears, Actuators | Automation of repetitive sampling tasks. |

